{"tid":2123223,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"印度方艙醫院14歲女患者遭性侵　疑犯同為確診病人","createTime":"2020-07-24T13:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T09:48:00.000Z","uid":159448,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"86b7982bfe087fe21250bfd9d876a8062875d029","tid":2123223,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:11:45.000Z","msg":"印度警方7月23日表示，國內最大的治療新冠肺炎患者設施、印度版「方艙醫院」發生強姦案，一名已確診新型冠狀病毒肺炎（COVID-19）的14歲女子懷疑遭另一名患者性侵。<br />\n事發於薩達爾&mdash;帕特爾新冠肺炎護理中心（Sardar Patel Covid Care Centre），《今日印度》<br />\n<br />\n（IndiaToday）報道，一名19歲男子15日晚跟着前往洗手間的受害人，之後在裏面性侵她，另一名同夥則在旁用手機錄下過程。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，正進一步調查此事，現時已逮捕並拘留這2名疑犯，也已沒收被告的手機，受害人亦已轉移到另一政府醫院。<br />\n<br />\n《印度斯坦時報》（Hindustan Times）則有另一說法，報道引述一名匿名的警方調查人員指，受害人與疑犯在醫院逗留期間變得熟悉，事發當天，犯罪嫌疑人以與受害者交談為由把她叫到醫院一個偏僻的地方，之後發生性侵事件。<br />\n<br />\n曾出現類似事件<br />\n<br />\n這已不是印度首次出現類似案件，孟買一間「方艙醫院」16日晚上也發生性侵案，一名40歲女子在檢疫中心隔離期間遭25歲男子進入房間性侵。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/502185/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%89%99%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A214%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5-%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E5%90%8C%E7%82%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F502185%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%2589%2599%25E9%2586%25AB%25E9%2599%25A214%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%2580%25A7%25E4%25BE%25B5-%25E7%2596%2591%25E7%258A%25AF%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=u6RaX9rkx0MxONw5VJESxfcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=a37087f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/502185/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E6%96%B9%E8%89%99%E9%86%AB%E9%99%A214%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E9%81%AD%E6%80%A7%E4%BE%B5-%E7%96%91%E7%8A%AF%E5%90%8C%E7%82%BA%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BA%BA</a>"},{"pid":"c60fa52480198eb3b7dfc40bce6ae0cc8be349b1","tid":2123223,"uid":31185,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:19:27.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbe4f664f5b6dfcaa673fe17c266a09444c9791","tid":2123223,"uid":83251,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:21:04.000Z","msg":"不意外,India!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44f23a6c320ce993f023abbf0445c5079309d9e","tid":2123223,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:21:45.000Z","msg":"唔錄手機應該告唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb74361fe4e9f4a0caee0608ee48e2f71b1ee932","tid":2123223,"uid":277186,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:22:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KEzS6JJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKEzS6JJ.jpg&h=42b02d0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b7bb72731e519f3730c82d57b31b0a962364cae","tid":2123223,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:24:22.000Z","msg":"一個14歲 1個40歲 年齡無分界限<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e3f7fa1853e778951258cbf9c9903ee0aba163","tid":2123223,"uid":137627,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"風化大國連死都要犯案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396332ce6fce5fd09b01cc57c378caf7ee9b39c7","tid":2123223,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8e3f7fa1853e778951258cbf9c9903ee0aba163","tid":2123223,"uid":137627,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T13:27:07.000Z","msg":"風化大國連死都要犯案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/g